    "en": {
      "name": "Mulcharmy Fuwaross",
      "effect": "If you control no cards (Quick Effect): You can discard this card; apply these effects this turn.\n\u25cf Each time your opponent Special Summons a monster(s) from the Deck and/or Extra Deck, immediately draw 1 card.\n\u25cf Once, during this End Phase, if the number of cards in your hand is more than the number of cards your opponent controls +6, you must randomly shuffle cards from your hand into the Deck so the number in your hand equals the number your opponent controls +6.\nYou can only activate 1 other \"Mulcharmy\" monster effect, the turn you activate this effect.",
      "official": false
    },
